{n}And for this brief moment, you look into the abyss that hides behind the name {g|LanternKing}'Lantern King'{/g}. And what is there? Light? Laughter? Bolts of lightning — or thoughts of an ancient mind, mighty and strange? You haven't the time to comprehend all you see, but you know one thing for true. The Lantern King is cursed.
The Lantern King is mortal. The punishment he heaped upon Nyrissa has returned to him, and taken his precious immortality.
It is your turn to speak!{/n}
